OL,3,CNatalie McNally considered breaking up
OL,4,Cwith murder accused, court hears
OL,6,FNatalie McNally sent messages
OL,7,Findicating she was considering
OL,8,Fbreaking up with a man now accused of
OL,9,Fher murder, Belfast Crown Court has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FThe murder trial also heard that
OL,13,FStephen McCullagh made a 39-minute
OL,14,Faudio recording in Ms McNally's
OL,15,Fparents' home just weeks after her
OL,16,Fdeath.
OL,18,FMs McNally, 32, was 15 weeks pregnant
OL,19,Fwhen she was killed at her home in
OL,20,FLurgan on December 18 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
