OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773667691
OL,3,CNatalie McNally considered breaking up
OL,4,Cwith murder accused, court hears
OL,6,FHer partner, Stephen McCullagh, 36, of
OL,7,FWoodland Gardens in Lisburn, is on
OL,8,Ftrial for her murder.
OL,10,FHe denies the charge.
OL,12,FThe jury in the trial was read agreed
OL,13,Fevidence on Friday morning, which
OL,14,Fincluded exchanges of messages between
OL,15,FMs McNally and other men in the months
OL,16,Fbefore she was killed.
OL,18,FThe court heard that on December 16
OL,19,Fshe had responded to a message from a
OL,20,Fman known as Male B and informed him
OL,21,Fshe was pregnant.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
