CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773667691
OL,3,CNatalie McNally considered breaking up
OL,4,Cwith murder accused, court hears
OL,6,FShe said: "I am single but still
OL,7,Fpregnant.
OL,9,F"I know it is not a typical situation
OL,10,Fbut I am delighted to have a baby by
OL,11,Fmyself."
OL,13,FMale B said: "Just think next
OL,14,FChristmas you'll be a mummy. How cool."
OL,16,FMs McNally replied: "I know, it's so
OL,17,Fexciting. My family are over the moon."
OL,19,FMs McNally had sent messages to
OL,20,Fanother man, Male C, on December 11.
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@AOUsD@HO]uD@NOUvD@gO]xD@UOUyD@
OL,26,AgO]
