OL,3,CNatalie McNally considered breaking up
OL,4,Cwith murder accused, court hears
OL,6,FShe said: "I just like doing my own
OL,7,Fthing and now I have to make plans all
OL,8,Fthe time with this person, can't be
OL,9,Fbothered."
OL,11,FMale C responded: "Are you going to
OL,12,Fbreak it up?"
OL,14,FShe said: "No, I wouldn't do it before
OL,15,FChristmas, that's just mean. I'll see
OL,16,Fhow I feel after the New Year."
OL,18,FIn a later message she added: "Maybe
OL,19,Fit will be OK. I just like my space,
OL,20,Fmaybe he will be happy enough giving
OL,21,Fme a few weeks by myself to chill.
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@JO]sD@SOUtD@MO]vD@KOUxD@_O]zD@
OL,26,A_OU
