OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773667691
OL,3,CNatalie McNally considered breaking up
OL,4,Cwith murder accused, court hears
OL,6,F"There's nothing wrong with him, I'm
OL,7,Fjust feeling a bit uneasy.
OL,9,F"Well, I'll make no rash decisions."
OL,11,FThe jury was then told McCullagh had
OL,12,Fcreated a note on his mobile phone on
OL,13,FNovember 8 which said Ms McNally had
OL,14,Fbeen speaking to her mother about what
OL,15,Fto do with her house if she moved in
OL,16,Fwith him.
OL,18,FIt read: "Could tell she is
OL,19,Fapprehensive as it is such a big
OL,20,Fchange, wants to be close to her
OL,21,Ffamily.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUqD@dO]zD@JOU
