OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773667691
OL,3,CNatalie McNally considered breaking up
OL,4,Cwith murder accused, court hears
OL,6,F"Sees this place as my house and not
OL,7,Fhers. I told her she can do to this
OL,8,Fplace whatever she likes as I trust
OL,9,Fher.
OL,11,F"Didn't acknowledge that I am putting
OL,12,Fwork in to making space for both her
OL,13,Fand the baby."
OL,15,FThe jury was then told McCullagh had
OL,16,Fconducted internet searches on
OL,17,FDecember 18 on Translink's website
OL,18,Fabout late-night bus and train
OL,19,Fservices to Lurgan and surrounding
OL,20,Fareas.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@NO]
