OL,3,CNatalie McNally considered breaking up
OL,4,Cwith murder accused, court hears
OL,6,FThe court also heard police had
OL,7,Flocated on McCullagh's phone an audio
OL,8,Frecording lasting 39 minutes and seven
OL,9,Fseconds which was made in January 2023
OL,10,Fin the McNally family home.
OL,12,FHolly McNally, who is married to Ms
OL,13,FMcNally's brother Niall, then gave
OL,14,Fwitness evidence.
OL,16,FShe told the court she had been in the
OL,17,FMcNally family home "most of the time"
OL,18,Fin the days after the murder.
OL,26,@yD@UOUyD@fO]
