OL,3,CNatalie McNally considered breaking up
OL,4,Cwith murder accused, court hears
OL,6,FShe said: "I saw it was him and I said
OL,7,F'oh God he is back, I wonder is he OK.'
OL,9,F"I got up and went to the front door
OL,10,Fto meet him."
OL,12,FThe witness said he told her he had
OL,13,Fforgotten his mobile phone.
OL,15,FHe retrieved it and left, the court
OL,16,Fheard.
